1. git branch stage origin/stage
                                //branch 'stage' set up to track 'origin/stage'.
                                //it's some like downstream
                                //we link them reversely!

Note: we can use direct command by switch
      "git switch -C stage origin/stage"

2. we commit current file on stage branch
   and push it to github

Note: some developer can push another commit on stage branch simultaneously
      on pushing we need resolve the conflicts
      (they should do too)

3. for simulate other developer working
   we add step 3 on github directly (on stage branch)

