Note: "git remote prune origin"
      if a branch was deleted on server (by github or other developer)
      but it still exist on our origin  (git branch -r)
      we can remove these kind of branches by "PRUNE"
                                                       "git remote prune origin"

SUMMARY: we always need to create branches manually
